headline: Why Hub Group (HUBG) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of logistics solutions provider Hub Group (NASDAQ:HUBG) jumped 2.6% in the afternoon session after Raymond James upgraded the stock's rating to 'Outperform' from 'Market Perform' and set a new price target of $40.

headline: Wall Street bonanza boosts profits at JPMorgan and Goldman
summary: A Wall Street dealmaking bonanza in the third quarter helped boost profits at JPMorgan Chase and Goldman Sachs as the country’s largest banks raked in higher revenues from investment banking and trading.
